message.entry: FINDBOUNDS: forward_fcn and inverse_fcn fields of TFORM cannot both be empty.
FINDBOUNDS: 搜索过程失败；将返回 OUTBOUNDS = INBOUNDS。
FINDBOUNDS: Search procedure failed with a mixed-dimensionality TFORM.
FINDBOUNDS: 第一个输入参数必须为 TFORM 结构体。
FINDBOUNDS: First input argument must be a 1-by-1 TFORM struct.
FINDBOUNDS: Input and output dimensions of TFORM must be the same.
FINDBOUNDS: INBOUNDS must be a 2-by-NUM_DIMS numeric matrix.
FINDBOUNDS: INBOUNDS must contain only finite values.
